{"tid":2320703,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是靚午 角煮豚肉飯","createTime":"2020-12-11T04:12:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-11T15:32:07.000Z","uid":33359,"like":73,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"4e8e349dff9d7263a253bf3a852d652ad4a288bc","tid":2320703,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T04:12:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T3CNgCj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT3CNgCj.jpg&h=8766baee&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7rdD7J9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7rdD7J9.jpg&h=57d9f6f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n講吓味道先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n豬肉煮得相當好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n表層有少少焦糖化<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食到有焦香味<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n豬肉味都好足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n油脂香氣有散發到出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n溏心強都極得唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有強香有醬香<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講吓缺點<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n菜絲同啲枝豆粒既草青味有啲勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n應該要處理吓先加入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一路食住一路聞到啲草青味真係唔是幾開胃<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n飯上面既醬汁偏少<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n基本上只係豬肉上面流落去既汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無另外加汁係飯到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以個飯食落有少少乾<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食落個腦下垂體好c伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBtw出餐好咗好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n準時拎到餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1f290518f644fe1963a50f7fe61c3cb3d15b2a1","tid":2320703,"uid":313974,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T04:12:46.000Z","msg":"豚肉師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3342fd623df5fe0dc30ea40cd4901758c82031ec","tid":2320703,"uid":59703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T04:12:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce2f474d7476a12c7c27fb815a0501c6ccc05d90","tid":2320703,"uid":24682,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T04:12:51.000Z","msg":"Mewe師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73818f24739e3e638696e98867199ba1a1ea1771","tid":2320703,"uid":301917,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T04:12:54.000Z","msg":"觀塘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69a91eb6779a6a568e82573b8fd008283513ad64","tid":2320703,"uid":374184,"like":276,"dislike":2,"score":274,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T04:12:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"01052f296134b65e8e27893391d5787e6c0c2cdb","tid":2320703,"uid":207009,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T04:13:02.000Z","msg":"今日遲左食喎印仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be228a03a3b763041c529f7b53cbac66a80f07b1","tid":2320703,"uid":200253,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"69a91eb6779a6a568e82573b8fd008283513ad64","tid":2320703,"uid":374184,"like":276,"dislike":2,"score":274,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2